The rogue mask is a piece of armour, which provides +5 bonuses to all Defence types. The mask is similar in design to a balaclava. The mask cannot be crafted, is untradeable, and can be stored in the costume room of a player-owned house.

There is a 1/8 chance of obtaining a piece of rogue equipment when a player successfully cracks the safe at the end of the Rogues' Den maze.
